column5: Went back to secret lake #234 and got into some really chunky walleye with my buddy.    Steady action once the bite started around 3:30pm.    Here is some video  from earlier in the week too.
Do you fish Lac Seul at all ?
All the time in the boat, not on the ice, it’s a bit far to go and lots of current I’m not familiar with which is a good thing to know on the ice.
